<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1951-12-14T00:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1948-09-09T00:00:00-05:00" n="425" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d425">
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                            </head>
                            <p>On June 13, 1950, after considerable debate in the Bundestag,
                                Chancellor Adenauer accepted Associate membership for the Federal
                                Republic in the Council of Europe (<hi rend="italic">Documents on
                                    International Affairs</hi>, 1949–1950, pp. 359–362).</p>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>